    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "Job",
        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 19,
        "summary": "Job tells of the ills that have befallen him and then testifies, I know that my Redeemer lives\u2014Job prophesies that he will be resurrected and that in his flesh he will see God.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "Then Job answered and said,",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "How long will ye vex my soul, and break me in pieces with words?",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "These ten times have ye reproached me: ye are not ashamed that ye make yourselves strange to me.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 58,
                        "end": 62
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And be it indeed that I have erred, mine error remaineth with myself.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 17,
                        "end": 21
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "If indeed ye will magnify yourselves against me, and plead against me my reproach:",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 26,
                        "end": 36
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Know now that God hath overthrown me, and hath compassed me with his net.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Behold, I cry out of wrong, but I am not heard: I cry aloud, but there is no judgment.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0justice.",
                        "start": 77,
                        "end": 85
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 65,
                        "end": 73
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "He hath fenced up my way that I cannot pass, and he hath set darkness in my paths.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "He hath stripped me of my glory, and taken the crown from my head.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 53,
                        "end": 57
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "He hath destroyed me on every side, and I am gone: and mine hope hath he removed like a tree.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "He hath also kindled his wrath against me, and he counteth me unto him as one of his enemies.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 74,
                        "end": 80
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "His troops come together, and raise up their way against me, and encamp round about my tabernacle.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0tent.",
                        "start": 87,
                        "end": 97
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "He hath put my brethren far from me, and mine acquaintance are verily estranged from me.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "My kinsfolk have failed, and my familiar friends have forgotten me.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 31:11 (11\u201312).",
                        "start": 54,
                        "end": 63
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "They that dwell in mine house, and my maids, count me for a stranger: I am an alien in their sight.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "I called my servant, and he gave me no answer; I entreated him with my mouth.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 33,
                        "end": 35
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "My breath is strange to my wife, though I entreated for the children's sake of mine own body.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0spirit.",
                        "start": 3,
                        "end": 9
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 71,
                        "end": 75
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Yea, young children despised me; I arose, and they spake against me.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "All my inward friends abhorred me: and they whom I loved are turned against me.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0intimate.",
                        "start": 7,
                        "end": 13
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "My bone cleaveth to my skin and to my flesh, and I am escaped with the skin of my teeth.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Have pity upon me, have pity upon me, O ye my friends; for the hand of God hath touched me.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Friendship.",
                        "start": 46,
                        "end": 53
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Job 1:11.",
                        "start": 63,
                        "end": 67
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Why do ye persecute me as God, and are not satisfied with my flesh?",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "IE\u00a0the state of my body, or suffering.",
                        "start": 58,
                        "end": 66
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Oh that my words were now written! oh that they were printed in a book!",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "That they were graven with an iron pen and lead in the rock for ever!",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For I know that my redeemer liveth, and that he shall stand at the latter day upon the earth:",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Loyalty; Testimony.",
                        "start": 6,
                        "end": 10
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Foreordained; Jesus Christ, Redeemer.",
                        "start": 19,
                        "end": 27
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Second Coming.",
                        "start": 45,
                        "end": 47
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Resurrection.",
                        "start": 54,
                        "end": 59
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 11,
                        "end": 15
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 40,
                        "end": 44
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 74,
                        "end": 77
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And though after my skin worms destroy this body, yet in my flesh shall I see God:",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Flesh; Immortality; Resurrection.",
                        "start": 60,
                        "end": 65
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Jn. 3:2.",
                        "start": 74,
                        "end": 77
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 10
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 25,
                        "end": 30
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 44,
                        "end": 49
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Whom I shall see for myself, and mine eyes shall behold, and not another; though my reins be consumed within me.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 74,
                        "end": 80
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "But ye should say, Why persecute we him, seeing the root of the matter is found in me?",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Be ye afraid of the sword: for wrath bringeth the punishments of the sword, that ye may know there is a judgment.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 37,
                        "end": 45
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 93,
                        "end": 101
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    }
}